Title: Libratone One Click Portable Bluetooth Speaker
Body (HTML):
TRANSFORM YOUR SPEAKER WITH A CLICK!

Meet the Swiss Army Knife of Speakers: innovative design, unbeatable sound quality and a range of accessories that click on and off.


Dimensions: 12 × 4.1 × 20.5 cm


Power: More than 12 hours playback


App:  Available for download through Apple App Store and Google Play Store.


Personalization: Changeable frame – allowing you to change colour and style. The click frame supports different attachments.


2 phone connections: Connect two phones and take turns playing music.


Bluetooth +1: Pair two Libratone Bluetooth speakers to play together.

12+ hour rechargeable battery, charges via USB, pair 2 speakers together, speakerphone, intuitive touch-control interface and and easy to use app
From the AUTHORIZED DEALER.
WARRANTY if it's a defective piece.

Description
 
ONE Click is redefining portable speakers for life on-the-go with its innovative design, changeable accessories and unbeatable sound quality. ONE Click comes with two interchangeable attachments in the form of a strap or a lockable hook making it easy to adapt to however you want to attach or place it.

Amazing sound with more bass than other portable Bluetooth speakers - Like all Libratone speakers, ONE Click is specifically tuned to provide a full range of sound without compromise, delivering more bass than other portable Bluetooth speakers, full midrange and crisp treble. 360-degree sound projects audio in every direction meaning wherever the speaker is placed, everyone will have an equally clear, direct acoustic experience. 
 Splash Proof - A design that withstands weather changes and splashes of water. ONE Click’s protective rubber frame shields it from any surface - wet or dry, and its unique fabric cover protects its elements from the elements. With an IPX-4 splash proof rating, you don’t have to worry if water hits your ONE Click while in the canoe, by the pool, or on a hike in sudden rain. 

 “Paperback book” shape - This shape makes it convenient to take anywhere. About the size of a paperback book, ONE Click fits naturally in your hand and can be conveniently slipped into a purse or bag.
 
Clever accessories - Comes with two clever, interchangeable hanging accessories for versatile adaptability on the go. An adjustable short handle and a handy U-shaped lock for hanging on a bike, a tree branch, boat, backpack or bookshelf.

Adapts to life on-the-go - With a click or two, you can change the way you carry, hang or wear ONE Click. An optional long strap makes it easy to wear while you hike or take a leisurely stroll.

Title: Libratone TOO Portable Bluetooth Speaker
Body (HTML):
Amazing 360-degree sound from a small form factor, with libratones signature blend of Deep bass, full mid-range and crisp treble
Convenient grab-and-go compact size
Splash proof design withstands weather changes and splashes of water
12+ hours of rechargeable battery life that charges via USB
Includes the ability to pair 2 speakers together with Bluetooth +1, speakerphone, intuitive touch-control interface and easy to use app.
From the AUTHORIZED DEALER.
WARRANTY if it's a defective piece.





Description
TOO is a playful, portable Bluetooth speaker with big sound packed into a convenient, diminutive grab-and-go package. Sized to fit easily into your bag or back pocket, TOO is specifically tuned to provide a full range of sound delivering uncompromised, impressive bass performance and 360-degree sound. With 12+ hours of rechargeable battery life and a splash proof design, TOO is the ultimate companion for life on-the-go. 
Amazing sound with more bass than other portable Bluetooth speakers - TOO is specifically tuned to provide a full range of sound without compromise, delivering more bass than other portable Bluetooth speakers, full midrange and crisp treble. 360-degree sound projects audio in every direction meaning wherever the speaker is placed, everyone will have an equally clear, direct acoustic experience.
Grab-and-go compact size - Slim like a bottle and small enough to fit neatly into the pocket of a backpack or handbag, TOO is one of the most lightweight, ultra-portable speakers on the market.
 

Splash Proof Design - TOO is splash proof and its rubber foot and sturdy frame shield it from any surface - wet or dry, while its unique fabric cover protects its elements from the elements.
 

12+ Hours of rechargeable battery life - With more than 12 hours of playback on a single charge, your TOO will always be by your side ready to play when you are!
  
Convenient carrying loop - The small looped handle that hangs off the edge of TOO is perfect for hanging off your finger, clipping to your backpack (or on anything) for convenient hands free listening.

Description
The new X9 PRO by Keep Out was born to be your best professional partner in all kinds of games, allows you to access extra options, such as running macros or combinations of features that contribute, surely a real advantage against your enemies. It has 9 programmable buttons, a 3 position polling rate adjustment switch and a scroll button with 2 positions, button profile switching, high quality Omron switches. Its Avago 9800 optical sensor lets you adjust up to 8200 DPI to get the most power for your games. Thanks to the “Keep Out” software, you can fully configure each and every one of the benefits that incorporates the X9PRO. You can create profiles for each game that you can switch easily and quickly.

Title: Jabra Sport Pace Wireless Headset in 3 Colors
Body (HTML):
Brand: Jabra
Color: Yellow, Red & Blue
Superior quality wireless sound & calls
Rapid charge
On-demand pace guidance
Perfect and secure fit

Description
Wireless sports earbuds with premium sound, secure fit and integrated training app to enhance any sport.
Superior quality wireless sound & calls
Free your workout from cables while being energised with rich, inspirational sound. With Jabra Sport Pace, you can enjoy up to 5 hours of music or talk time with an easy transition from listening to music to making and receiving calls. Easy connectivity to your Android or Apple iOS smartphone will give you the wireless freedom that you are looking for.
Rapid charge
Never again will you have to skip your workout or morning run due to not having charged your headphones. Jabra Sport Pace has a rapid charge feature, allowing you to charge up your headphones while you get ready. 15 minutes of charging provides you with 60 minutes of battery life.
On-demand pace guidance
Jabra Sport Pace is more than just musical motivation, it’s a training guide. With the integrated training app, Jabra Sport Life gives you motivational training tips and allows you to plan, monitor and evaluate your training.
Perfect and secure fit
Due to the ergonomic design, Jabra Sport Pace has incredibly light and comfortable headphones that won’t fall out or hurt your ears. Find your perfect fit with the three sets of EarGels included that are guaranteed to lock in and stay securely in place during your workout. Weighing a mere 16 grams (0.56 oz), you’ll hardly notice that you’re wearing headphones at all.
3-year warranty against sweat**
Jabra Sport Pace headphones are sweat, shock and weather resistant with an IP54 rating. They come with a 3-year limited warranty against failure from sweat damage (registration required**) allowing you to concentrate on your workout in confidence. The reflective cord helps make you visible when running at night.
Jabra's Sport Life™ app
Jabra Sport Pace is more than just music motivation; it’s a training guide.
The integrated training app, Jabra Sport Life app, gives you motivational training tips and lets you plan, monitor and evaluate your training.

Headset Profile

Music
HD Voice

Standby Time: Up to 216 hours

Description
Make the everyday a little easier with classic, functionality of Jabra Classic. But make no mistake - behind the surface it is still powerful. Jabra Classic is designed for all-day hands free wearing with multiple wearing styles ensuring a perfect fit with your ear. The headset features Voice guidance that helps you pair devices and tells you when it’s when its time to recharge and announcing incoming calls – all hands free. 

 ONLY THE MOST NECESSARY FEATURES 

Jabra Classic is as straightforward as headsets come. Besides the on-off slider, you have volume controls on the headset on the side and a centrally placed answer/end button on the front – all easy to reach and use.

 WIRELESS FREEDOM WITH ENTERTAINMENT

When you’ve got a lot of multimedia content on your mobile device - smartphone, tablet or mp3 player - you can easily stream it all to your Bluetooth headset for when you’re on the go or in your car. 
 
THE HEADSET THAT TAKES POWER NAPS
Headsets need power naps too. The battery saving mode in Jabra Classic turns the headset off after having been disconnected from your mobile device for a full hour. And to wake your Jabra Classic up again, just press the answer/end button.  

 CUSTOM FIT TO YOUR EAR 

Jabra Classic is designed for all-day hands free wearing. You can wear it with or without the earhook, or alternatively with the Ultimate Comfort Eargels™ that mold softly to your ear at all times.

Simple, traditional design with three color options
On/off slider for intuitive handling 
Voice guidance – tells you how to pair your device, your battery- and connection status
Wear it all day with the earhook or ergonomically-designed EarGels™
HD voice* for better sound experience
Power Nap - battery saving mode
Wireless streaming of your favorite multimedia – GPS, music & podcasts (A2DP enabled devices)
Up to 9 hours talk time and up to 9 days standby time

45 DEGREE SMART PLUG
The 45 degree angle protects your plug from falling out from the slightest tug, we all hate that. The angle locks it in while still keeping a low profile.

These earbuds have an ergonomic design that give your ears maximum comfort. Now you can keep on rock'n for hours and hours with no discomfort.

Not all ear holes are created equal in size, so we give you 3 different sizes: Small, Medium & Large. Come across a head shrinker? We've got you covered.

FLAT CORD

HANDS FREE
This product has a mic/track control so you don't have to pull out your music player to change the song or answer a call.

We want you to hear the music the way it's intended to be heard; undistorted. You'll hear the music in it's original state. The way the artist intended it to be heard.
NOISE ISOLATION
Don't put up with listening to that loud mouth or screaming kid. Plug in & Rock out undisturbed with our noise isolation headphones. You'll be glad that you did.

                                    Description
                                Pull off your ultra high-res projects with the world’s fastest desktop storage. Break open bottlenecks and tighten up 4K–6K video workflows with blistering Thunderbolt 3 speeds and a reliable, new industrial design.

Create at the speed of lightning

 

The very fastest I/O.


For the Bolt3, LaCie harnessed the breakthrough performance potential of the Thunderbolt 3 I/O and paired it with the absolute fastest SSDs on the market. With a pair of M.2 PCIe SSDs striped together into a 2 TB volume, the result is astonishing speeds of up to 2,800 MB/s.


For transfers in minutes, not hours.
 


That kind of speed slashes time off nearly every task in your post-production workflow. Ingest RAW footage from RED® or Blackmagic® cinema cameras in a fraction of the time. Transcode 4/5/6K footage much faster using Adobe® Premiere® Pro or DaVinci Resolve. Then transfer a terabyte of footage from the Bolt3 to RAID storage—such as the LaCie 12big Thunderbolt 3 — in minutes instead of hours.



More speed. More pixels. More possibilities.

The USB-C that does it all.

Thunderbolt 3 brings Thunderbolt performance to USB-C connectivity at electrifying speeds of up to 40 Gb/s, creating a single compact port that does it all. Thunderbolt 3 permits daisy chaining and provides four times the data and twice the video bandwidth of any other cable, while also supplying power.

Compatible with Thunderbolt and Thunderbolt 2
It’s possible to connect the Bolt3 to devices with previous generations of Thunderbolt. Just use a Thunderbolt 3 (USB-C) to Thunderbolt 2 adaptor (sold separately). 

To level up your workspace.

This means you can daisy chain one USB-C (USB 3.1) or up to five Thunderbolt 3 devices, connect dual 4K displays, and even power a compatible laptop**— all through a single USB-C cable connected to your computer. With two 4K displays, you can spread out your workspace by dedicating one display to your timeline and the other to previewing 4K footage, for example. Thunderbolt 3 delivers double the performance and versatility of any other interface.

Built for dependability, from the outside in.

The LaCie Bolt3 is brilliantly engineered for the long term — from the enclosure to the internal components — to endure intensive storage tasks.

Aluminium enclosure

Each product is individually Computer Numerical Control machined from solid aluminium blocks for rigid durability and heat dissipation.

Title: Fiesta Crafts Magnetic Star Chart Extra Large
Body (HTML):
Gender: Unisex
Age: 3+ Yrs
Product Length Dimensions: 43 x 38 cm





Description
This wonderfully colourful Extra-large star chart for 2 children will encourage them to do the tasks set for them. It’s so simple to use; parents and children set the tasks - there are 20 magnetic pieces to choose from or you could use the dry wipe marker to write your own - ranging from going to bed on time, doing homework, tidying up toys or brushing teeth. And of course, you’ll need to choose the reward for reaching the target! The board itself is also magnetic, so easily attaches to metal surfaces, such as traditional fridges, or can be pinned to a wall.
For each child you choose a colour and write in the target for how many stars must be achieved in a week. You can place the ‘Target’ marker to show each child how far up the points ‘ladder’ they need to climb to receive their reward.
Every time your child successfully completes a task, they receive a star and will love to move their ‘Monkey’ marker up the ladder to their goal.
The Extra-large Star Chart is bright and engaging, and above all, fully interactive. It can be hung on the wall so it’s visible to everyone. Includes dry wipe pen.

Title: Fiesta Crafts Kids Magnetic Small My Calendar
Body (HTML):
Gender: Unisex
Age: 3+ Yrs
Product Length Dimensions: 42 x 54 cm


Board is magnetic - attach to fridges or other metallic surfaces.
A wonderful daily activity; children love to change the date and look out of the window to make their own forecast, placing one of the shaped weather pieces on the chart. My Calendar measures 20 x 26 cm and has 38 magnetic pieces. Months are coloured to match the seasons. Has a full magnetic backing so can be positioned on a fridge or can be pinned to a wall.
When it comes to learning all about the days of the week, months of the year and the weather, the easy to use My Magnetic Calendar is both educational and fun. Children can learn how to put the months in sequence, they can update the day of the week and the date every day, and can monitor the weather and update their chart as it changes. A fun daily activity for children aged 3-12, this also makes a splendid wall decoration to brighten up bedroom, playroom or classroom. Popular with adults too, the Magnetic My Calendar can often be found as a proud centrepiece in the kitchen. Every morning, children delight in changing the date pieces and are eager to peer out of the window to give their ‘forecast’ using the delightfully illustrated colour pieces in the special ‘Weather’ section. 
My Calendar has over 40 magnetic pieces. The board can also be attached to the wall via adhesive pads or pins through the pre-cut fixing holes.

Title: Fiesta Crafts Magnetic Fractions Board
Body (HTML):
Gender: Unisex
Age: 3+ Yrs
Product Length Dimensions: 18 x 25 cm                                     
                                    
                                                                                    
                            
                            
                                    Description
                                Fractions, percentages and decimals can be hard to understand, but these reversible magnetic pieces make it so much easier by being so visual and fun to work with. Simply turn over the pieces to see that 1/4th is the same as 0.25. Line them up on the board to see that 3 of them make 3/4 etc. Use the board to fill in sections of a shape or units and use the pieces to give the right answers. Magnetic Fractions is part of a new range of educational toys which has been designed to encourage children to stay tuned in even when the nature of the game is to learn. The magnetic board has been designed to show how one figure equates to the same in percentage or decimal terms, for example that 1/5th is the same as 20% and 0.2. The fractions pack includes a magnetic, wipe-clean board, pen, and activities to help guide children along and encourage their development in basic numeracy. Model Number: T-2679

My Calendar soft fabric wall hanging range from Fiesta are fabulous for helping children learn about days, dates and months. They also make splendid wall decorations to brighten up bedroom, playroom or classroom. Popular with adults too, Fiesta’s Wall Hangings can often be found as a proud centrepiece in the kitchen. Every morning, children delight in changing the embroidered date pieces and are particularly raring to peer out of the window to give their ‘forecast’ using the illustrated colour coded pieces in the special ‘Weather’ section. Both the main wall hanging and moveable pieces are embroidered and stuffed giving them a charming soft-toy cushiony feel.
A continuing best-seller for over 20 years, Fiesta’s fabric calendars bring warmth and joy wherever they are placed. And they are long-lasting too, becoming a family ‘heirloom’ many families have had their charts for many years; each child has grown up with this in their bedroom. And spares are available from Fiesta’s website just in case a piece gets lost!
Grown ups in the house will (secretly) love the learning that is happening; helping children better understand the tricky-to-grasp concept of days and dates, especially when they are counting down to birthdays and holidays.

Title: Fiesta Crafts Vehicles Threading T-2807 Kids DIY Arts & Craft Kit
Body (HTML): No activity is better placed to help develop fine motor skills than threading, a task that not only helps to improve concentration, but hand-eye coordination too. Teaching children to carefully thread laces through the correct holes to finish off a picture, or combining various pieces to make their own weird and wonderful creations is not only fun but educational too. Getting them to figure out how to follow the correct line to complete the right picture will also encourage them to see tasks through from beginning to end, while the bright colours and shapes will also help to develop their foundation years learning.
